Experience the celebration at Kangra held on 2 May 2019! Bongani Khumalo – Director of Unyenzi Coal; Dr Sakhile Ngobo – Director of Canyon Coal; Mpumelo Mkhabela – Chairman of Menar; Xolile Mankayi – Social Licence Manager for Menar; Isaac Mbanani from the National Union of Mineworkers; Vuslat Bayoglu – Managing Director of Menar; and Cllr Vusi Motha – Mayor of Mkhondo Local Municipality addressed those in attendance.